                       FROM sim_hr_employee emp
                       left join sim_users u on u.uid = emp.uid
                       left join sim_hr_employeestatus emps on emps.employeestatus_id = emp.employee_status
                       left join sim_hr_jobposition jop on jop.jobposition_id = emp.jobposition_id
                       left join sim_hr_department dep on dep.department_id = emp.department_id
                       left join sim_hr_employeegroup empg on empg.employeegroup_id = emp.employeegroup_id

                       left join sim_maritalstatus ms on ms.maritalstatus_id = emp.marital_status
                       left join sim_country co on co.country_id = emp.employee_citizenship
                       left join sim_races rac on rac.races_id = emp.races_id
                       left join sim_religion rel on rel.religion_id = emp.religion_id

             emp.employeegroup_id ,emp.department_id, dp.department_name , apr.appraisalline_date, bal.leave_total, ad.adjustment_total from
            (SELECT employee_name,employee_id, employee_no, employee_joindate, employee_confirmdate, employeegroup_id ,
                    department_id, leavetype_name, leavetype_id,employee_citizenship,marital_status
            from sim_hr_employee , sim_hr_leavetype where sim_hr_employee.isactive!=0 and sim_hr_leavetype.isactive!=0) emp
            left join sim_hr_employeegroup emg on emg.employeegroup_id = emp.employeegroup_id
            left join sim_hr_department dp on dp.department_id = emp.department_id
            left join (SELECT appraisalline_date, employee_id FROM sim_hr_appraisalline WHERE appraisalline_id in
                      (SELECT MAX(appraisalline_id) as lastedappraisal_id from sim_hr_appraisalline group by employee_id)) apr on apr.employee_id=emp.employee_id
            left join (SELECT leavetype_id, sum(leave_day) as leave_total , employee_id FROM `sim_hr_leave` where workflowlatest_id=2 group by employee_id, leavetype_id ) bal on bal.employee_id=emp.employee_id and emp.leavetype_id = bal.leavetype_id
            left join (SELECT a.leavetype_id, sum(a.leaveadjustmentline_totalday) as adjustment_total , a.employee_id, b.workflowlatest_id , b.leaveadjustment_id
                       FROM `sim_hr_leaveadjustmentline` a join sim_hr_leaveadjustment b on a.leaveadjustment_id = b.leaveadjustment_id where b.workflowlatest_id =2
                      group by employee_id, leavetype_id) ad on ad.employee_id=emp.employee_id and emp.leavetype_id = ad.leavetype_id
             WHERE emp.employee_id >0 AND emp.employee_id = 1 ORDER BY emp.employee_name, emp.leavetype_name ASC;

             emp.employeegroup_id ,emp.department_id, dp.department_name , apr.appraisalline_date, bal.leave_total, ad.adjustment_total from
            (SELECT employee_name,employee_id, employee_no, employee_joindate, employee_confirmdate, employeegroup_id ,
                    department_id, leavetype_name, leavetype_id,employee_citizenship,marital_status
            from sim_hr_employee , sim_hr_leavetype where sim_hr_employee.isactive!=0 and sim_hr_leavetype.isactive!=0) emp
            left join sim_hr_employeegroup emg on emg.employeegroup_id = emp.employeegroup_id
            left join sim_hr_department dp on dp.department_id = emp.department_id
            left join (SELECT appraisalline_date, employee_id FROM sim_hr_appraisalline WHERE appraisalline_id in
                      (SELECT MAX(appraisalline_id) as lastedappraisal_id from sim_hr_appraisalline group by employee_id)) apr on apr.employee_id=emp.employee_id
            left join (SELECT leavetype_id, sum(leave_day) as leave_total , employee_id FROM `sim_hr_leave` where workflowlatest_id=2 group by employee_id, leavetype_id ) bal on bal.employee_id=emp.employee_id and emp.leavetype_id = bal.leavetype_id
            left join (SELECT a.leavetype_id, sum(a.leaveadjustmentline_totalday) as adjustment_total , a.employee_id, b.workflowlatest_id , b.leaveadjustment_id
                       FROM `sim_hr_leaveadjustmentline` a join sim_hr_leaveadjustment b on a.leaveadjustment_id = b.leaveadjustment_id where b.workflowlatest_id =2
                      group by employee_id, leavetype_id) ad on ad.employee_id=emp.employee_id and emp.leavetype_id = ad.leavetype_id
             WHERE emp.employee_id >0 ORDER BY emp.employee_name, emp.leavetype_name ASC;

		from sim_groups g 
		inner join sim_groups_users_link gul on g.groupid=gul.groupid
		inner join sim_users u on gul.uid=u.uid
		inner join sim_group_permission gp on gp.gperm_groupid=g.groupid
		inner join sim_modules m on gp.gperm_itemid=m.mid

		inner join sim_window w on gsp.window_id=w.window_id
		where m.mid=64 and w.filename='employee.php' and w.isdeleted=0

		w.window_name, gsp.iswriteperm ,w.seqno,w.filename,w.windowsetting
		from sim_groups g 
		inner join sim_groups_users_link gul on g.groupid=gul.groupid
		inner join sim_users u on gul.uid=u.uid
		inner join sim_group_permission gp on gp.gperm_groupid=g.groupid
		inner join sim_modules m on gp.gperm_itemid=m.mid
		inner join sim_permission gsp on gsp.groupid=g.groupid
		inner join sim_window w on gsp.window_id=w.window_id
		where m.mid=64 and w.filename='employee.php' and w.isdeleted=0
                and gp.gperm_name='module_read' and u.uid=1
                and ( gsp.validuntil = '0000-00-00' OR gsp.validuntil >= '2010-08-05') order by gsp.iswriteperm DESC

10/08/05 10:37:11(4): SQL: SELECT wt.workflowtransaction_datetime,ws.workflowstatus_name,usr.name,wt.workflowtransaction_feedback
                        FROM sim_workflowtransaction wt
                        INNER JOIN sim_workflow wf ON wt.workflow_id = wf.workflow_id
                        INNER JOIN sim_workflowstatus ws ON wt.workflowstatus_id = ws.workflowstatus_id
                        INNER JOIN sim_workflowtransactionhistory wh ON wt.workflowtransaction_id = wh.workflowtransaction_id
                        INNER JOIN sim_users usr ON wh.uid = usr.uid
                        WHERE wf.workflow_code = 'GENERCLAIM'
                        AND wt.primarykey_value = '0'
                        ORDER BY wt.workflowtransaction_datetime DESC

                        FROM sim_workflowtransaction wt
                        INNER JOIN sim_workflow wf ON wt.workflow_id = wf.workflow_id
                        INNER JOIN sim_workflowstatus ws ON wt.workflowstatus_id = ws.workflowstatus_id
                        INNER JOIN sim_workflowtransactionhistory wh ON wt.workflowtransaction_id = wh.workflowtransaction_id
                        INNER JOIN sim_users usr ON wh.uid = usr.uid
                        WHERE wf.workflow_code = 'LEAVE'
                        AND wt.primarykey_value = '0'
                        ORDER BY wt.workflowtransaction_datetime DESC

                        INNER JOIN sim_workflowstatus ws ON wt.workflowstatus_id = ws.workflowstatus_id
                        INNER JOIN sim_workflowtransactionhistory wh ON wt.workflowtransaction_id = wh.workflowtransaction_id

		inner join sim_window w on gsp.window_id=w.window_id
		where m.mid=64 and w.filename='employee.php' and w.isdeleted=0
                and gp.gperm_name='module_read' and u.uid=1

10/08/05 11:11:37(4): SQL: SELECT wt.workflowtransaction_datetime,ws.workflowstatus_name,usr.name,wt.workflowtransaction_feedback
                        FROM sim_workflowtransaction wt
                        INNER JOIN sim_workflow wf ON wt.workflow_id = wf.workflow_id
                        INNER JOIN sim_workflowstatus ws ON wt.workflowstatus_id = ws.workflowstatus_id
                        INNER JOIN sim_workflowtransactionhistory wh ON wt.workflowtransaction_id = wh.workflowtransaction_id
                        INNER JOIN sim_users usr ON wh.uid = usr.uid
                        WHERE wf.workflow_code = 'GENERCLAIM'
                        AND wt.primarykey_value = '0'
                        ORDER BY wt.workflowtransaction_datetime DESC

		from sim_groups g 
		inner join sim_groups_users_link gul on g.groupid=gul.groupid
		inner join sim_users u on gul.uid=u.uid
		inner join sim_group_permission gp on gp.gperm_groupid=g.groupid
		inner join sim_modules m on gp.gperm_itemid=m.mid
		inner join sim_permission gsp on gsp.groupid=g.groupid
		inner join sim_window w on gsp.window_id=w.window_id
		where m.mid=64 and w.filename='employee.php' and w.isdeleted=0
                and gp.gperm_name='module_read' and u.uid=1

10/08/05 12:10:39(4): showApprovallistGrid SQL: SELECT
                wt.*, emp.employee_name, emp.employee_no,
                wf.workflow_name,ws.workflowstatus_name
                FROM sim_workflowtransaction wt
                LEFT JOIN sim_hr_employee emp ON wt.person_id = emp.employee_id
                INNER JOIN sim_workflow wf ON wt.workflow_id = wf.workflow_id
                INNER JOIN sim_workflowstatus ws ON wt.workflowstatus_id = ws.workflowstatus_id
                 WHERE wt.workflowtransaction_id>0 AND (wt.target_uid = 1 OR 1 IN (wt.targetparameter_name)
                        OR 1 IN (SELECT uid FROM sim_groups_users_link WHERE groupid = wt.target_groupid)
                        )  AND wt.iscomplete = 0 

                ORDER BY wt.created DESC

10/08/05 13:16:35(4): With SQL: select distinct(w.window_id) as window_id,
		w.window_name, gsp.iswriteperm ,w.seqno,w.filename,w.windowsetting
		from sim_groups g 
		inner join sim_groups_users_link gul on g.groupid=gul.groupid
		inner join sim_users u on gul.uid=u.uid
		inner join sim_group_permission gp on gp.gperm_groupid=g.groupid
		inner join sim_modules m on gp.gperm_itemid=m.mid
		inner join sim_permission gsp on gsp.groupid=g.groupid
		inner join sim_window w on gsp.window_id=w.window_id
		where m.mid=64 and w.filename='leave.php' and w.isdeleted=0
                and gp.gperm_name='module_read' and u.uid=1
                and ( gsp.validuntil = '0000-00-00' OR gsp.validuntil >= '2010-08-05') order by gsp.iswriteperm DESC

10/08/05 13:58:35(4): showApprovallistGrid SQL: SELECT
                wt.*, emp.employee_name, emp.employee_no,
                wf.workflow_name,ws.workflowstatus_name
                FROM sim_workflowtransaction wt
                LEFT JOIN sim_hr_employee emp ON wt.person_id = emp.employee_id
                INNER JOIN sim_workflow wf ON wt.workflow_id = wf.workflow_id
                INNER JOIN sim_workflowstatus ws ON wt.workflowstatus_id = ws.workflowstatus_id
                 WHERE wt.workflowtransaction_id>0 AND (wt.target_uid = 1 OR 1 IN (wt.targetparameter_name)
                        OR 1 IN (SELECT uid FROM sim_groups_users_link WHERE groupid = wt.target_groupid)
                        )  AND wt.iscomplete = 0 

                ORDER BY wt.created DESC

10/08/05 14:20:58(4): showApprovallistGrid SQL: SELECT
                wt.*, emp.employee_name, emp.employee_no,
                wf.workflow_name,ws.workflowstatus_name
                FROM sim_workflowtransaction wt
                LEFT JOIN sim_hr_employee emp ON wt.person_id = emp.employee_id
                INNER JOIN sim_workflow wf ON wt.workflow_id = wf.workflow_id
                INNER JOIN sim_workflowstatus ws ON wt.workflowstatus_id = ws.workflowstatus_id
                 WHERE wt.workflowtransaction_id>0 AND (wt.target_uid = 1 OR 1 IN (wt.targetparameter_name)
                        OR 1 IN (SELECT uid FROM sim_groups_users_link WHERE groupid = wt.target_groupid)
                        )  AND wt.iscomplete = 0 

                ORDER BY wt.created DESC

		from sim_groups g 
		inner join sim_groups_users_link gul on g.groupid=gul.groupid
		inner join sim_users u on gul.uid=u.uid
		inner join sim_group_permission gp on gp.gperm_groupid=g.groupid
		inner join sim_modules m on gp.gperm_itemid=m.mid
		inner join sim_permission gsp on gsp.groupid=g.groupid
		inner join sim_window w on gsp.window_id=w.window_id
		where m.mid=68 and w.filename='index.php' and w.isdeleted=0
                and gp.gperm_name='module_read' and u.uid=1

10/08/05 14:21:25(4): showApprovallistGrid SQL: SELECT
                wt.*, emp.employee_name, emp.employee_no,
                wf.workflow_name,ws.workflowstatus_name
                FROM sim_workflowtransaction wt
                LEFT JOIN sim_hr_employee emp ON wt.person_id = emp.employee_id
                INNER JOIN sim_workflow wf ON wt.workflow_id = wf.workflow_id
                INNER JOIN sim_workflowstatus ws ON wt.workflowstatus_id = ws.workflowstatus_id
                 WHERE wt.workflowtransaction_id>0 AND (wt.target_uid = 1 OR 1 IN (wt.targetparameter_name)
                        OR 1 IN (SELECT uid FROM sim_groups_users_link WHERE groupid = wt.target_groupid)
                        )  AND wt.iscomplete = 0 

                ORDER BY wt.created DESC
